race.comment: Competitive contest. The penny has dropped for BARRELLING (5) who has put back-to-back wins together over this track and trip and is racing high on confidence. Gets the services of Thompson to navigate from the sticky draw and can play a major role with any luck in running. RAMP IT UP (2) boasts a win around this circuit and has saluted when second-up before. Should be hitting the line with gusto. CARRAVILLA (6) returned in good order with a solid Sunny Coast win and can go right on with the job now. HOT WINGS (8) has strung three wins together on the bounce and it's hard to knock mares in form. Has earned her shot at this level. LAST COMMAND (1) next best with the 3kg claim.
